==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionLinePerpendicular''' tool adds a cosmetic line perpendicular to another line through a vertex.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionLinePerpendicularExample.png|250px]]
{{Caption|On the right an added cosmetic perpendicular line}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the line attributes with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select a straight edge to determine the direction and the length of the line.
# Select a vertex to determine the position of the line.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionLinePerpendicular.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionLinePerpendicular|Add Cosmetic Perpendicular Line]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Centerlines/Threading → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionLinePerpendicular.svg|16px]] Add Cosmetic Perpendicular Line}} option from the menu.
# A cosmetic line is added.


